    <author initials="I." surname="Kouvelas" fullname="Isidor Kouvelas">
      <organization>Arista Networks</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="25" month="April" year="2016"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a hierarchical method of encoding Join/Prune attributes that provides a more efficient encoding when the same attribute values need to be specified for multiple sources in a PIM Join/Prune message.  This document updates RFC 5384 by renaming the encoding type registry specified there.</t>
    </abstract>
